As a proud Ambassador for @the_bhf I am supporting @sclub and British Heart Foundation in memory of Paul to put a Spotlight On hidden heart conditions. Together, we can raise awareness of heart and circulatory conditions and be part of research breakthroughs that could outsmart them for good. Please join us in remembering Paul and all those affected by hidden heart conditions, by showing your heart this September & October using #ShowYourHearts
